- snake game blueprint:

1. create the snake
    - giving the snake ability to move with listener controls
    - growing the snake when it eats something
    - have the snake be able to react to walls = game over
    - have the snake be able to react to itself = game over

2. create the food
    - the food must appear randomly
    - the food must disappear when snake eats it

3. create the scoreboard
    - update by 1 each time snake eats food



